TITLE: Episode 134 - Salting the Earth with Britt
DESCRIPTION: It's ladies' night. Cam is out this week, so Britt (a.k.a. @TweetsByBritt) is joining Jessica to talk about the absolute state of women and humanity these days. Between Aquama'am, Rachel Levine as Woman of the year, and the raging culture wars going on, there's a lot to talk about. Join us.
